snippet.title: AI Asylum Gameplay: Don't want to escape, in fact!
snippet.description:
🎮New game to play: AI Asylum
https://elijah-bleu.itch.io/aisylum

🔑 Unlocking Nora's room in the upgraded AI asylum! Enter and discover her captivating story! 🚪🔍 Collect items, uncover secrets, and attempt a daring escape! Can you make it out? 
Join us in this immersive journey through an extraordinary mental hospital and experience seamless interaction like never before! 🏥🎮
